>>> 	0 3 2 1 4 5 4 1 0 5 2 4 0 1 4 3
>>> 	2 5 0 1 4 3 5 0 3 2 1 2 5 0 3 2
>>> ].collect { :t |
>>> 	GrayCode(t)
>>> 	.isBeckettGrayCode
>>> }.allTrue
true
```

